Extended rd2html format library
	
rd2html-ext is an extended rd2html format library.
it provides the following function in addition to the original rd2html-lib.rb.

 * section no. at headline
 * enable <br> at textblock
 * reference extension
   + inline image
   + reference to ruby-list ml
   + reference to raa
 * native inline
   + any html inline can be inserted in rd!!
 * head element
   + any html elements in head element in rd!!